"You keep reminding yourself that we had a big lead at Valderrama; we had a big lead at Brookline, where we lost, and at Valderrama, where we scratched the nail", Bjorn said, pictured, after watching the Class of 2018 win 5-3 on Friday and lead 10-6 at Le Golf National yesterday.
So, history will show me and everyone on the team that this is not over.
You're going full speed ahead tomorrow.
